txt.en: The Great Goblin's throne has many challengers - all of whom must be defeated with haste if the threat of Goblin-town is to be quelled.
You have defeated the Great Goblins with haste
The Great Goblin's throne lies deep within Goblin-town. His reign must be brought to an end quickly if the Free Peoples of Middle-earth are to remain safe.
Defeat the Great Goblin in under 4 minutes
The Great Goblin and his minions must be defeated with great haste if the Free Peoples of Middle-earth are to remain safe.
